{"about_the_game":"It\u2019s the gold rush era. Native people attacked the Snake Canyon mine just after a few days when white men discovered ancient artifacts. Jack, an experienced bounty hunter, and White Eagle, a respected warrior among his people, are after the same artifacts for different reasons.<br><br>Switch between characters throughout the chapters, use unique, historical weapons, fight hundreds of men in a wide Old West world, and change the fate of the war.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dive into intense and varied combat encounters with a wide range of weapons. Each weapon introduces a unique mechanic and a new play style.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/WeaponsGIF.gif?t=1713267722\" /><br></li><li><strong>Survive, defend, infiltrate, or escape! Discover a new area and overcome a new challenge in each chapter.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/Environment2OPT.gif?t=1713267722\" /><br></li><li><strong>Witness the clash of two worlds through the eyes of different characters and unravel the mysterious powers of ancient artifacts.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/Story2.gif?t=1713267722\" /><br></li><li><strong>Unlock the Bounty Hunt after the main campaign and earn bounties when you kill in style and find timed bounty bags. Use the money to create unique weapon-enhancement combinations, and compete with other players to become a legend!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Experience a realistic and smooth VR interaction while using weapons and objects.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Choose from multiple movement and ease-of-use options designed for VR.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Follow the characters' epic stories through fully narrated and animated shorts.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Walk in delicately designed, Old West-inspired environments.</strong><br><strong>And much more!</strong><br><br><strong>Are you ready to embark on this epic adventure and prove your mettle in the wild, untamed West?</strong></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Small Favor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/c78c84cc9cd0e92d889e3d80d52b65309a49bdc5.jpg"},{"name":" Back in the Saddle Again","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/705b068c7b5187603ced5e348315a6b0d5037c37.jpg"},{"name":"Taming the Iron Horse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/c06e6456c1cae4a29318e32b0e9b0bc00fc327b5.jpg"},{"name":"Locked and Loaded","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/3d2c6105e16e187b55c696716b290408639e2728.jpg"},{"name":"A Dangerous Prisoner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/9bc2b78376ee8a054e06d3e9b9123acd9d0a996d.jpg"},{"name":"Snake Along","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/02eccb3fd5121008930d18364fdcce59021a3e84.jpg"},{"name":"Silent As Night","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/55caa95df2443791fe00d24d90337acdeae273fc.jpg"},{"name":"Mask Off","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/8fb03cb0905190ae60b26a2ba121ceffe80ca238.jpg"},{"name":"Taming the Beast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/b2ac456518c29c0987447d790cfa678f39c88a60.jpg"},{"name":"The Gambler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576420/048ba80e449aac856d40a756ba544ffad494466d.jpg"}],"total":37},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1713267722","background